ClassDesc: A data class representing a geographic location result from the fused location provider. All locations returned by @B_com#google#android#gms#location#LocationResult#getLocations_E@ are guaranteed to have a valid latitude, longitude, and UTC timestamp. On API level 17 or later they are also guaranteed to have elapsed real-time since boot. All other parameters are optional.
